<Window x:Class="WpfUI.AboutSystem"
        xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
        xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
        xmlns:local="clr-namespace:WpfUI"
        mc:Ignorable="d"
        Title="AboutSystem" Height="450" Width="600">
    <Grid>
        <Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <RowDefinition></RowDefinition>
            <RowDefinition></RowDefinition>
        </Grid.RowDefinitions>
        <TextBlock Width="500" Height="300" TextWrapping="Wrap">
            The automated system of calculation of materials for repair of the house is a system which is intended for automation of process of selection of quantity of materials during construction or repair. The system helps the user to simplify the calculation process.
            The purpose of creating an automated system (AS) - to automate the calculation of materials for home repairs.
            Purpose - to facilitate the calculation process and minimize the amount of actions and knowledge for constant work with the system.
            The system is designed for use on automated terminals, personal computers and laptops.
            The input data for the speaker are the parameters of buildings, premises, rooms, etc., which will be needed for further calculations to determine the amount of materials for repair.
            The source data is a list of possible materials (available for viewing without calculations) and a list of the number of materials that have been selected by the user for calculations.
            The system works in a simple mode of calculations, accepting the user's request for the necessary information, according to the input data.
        </TextBlock>
        <Grid Grid.Row="1">
            <Button Width="140" Height="40" FontSize="15" Click="ToMenu_Click">To Menu</Button>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
</Window>
